      <title>花旗校友计划无需 SEC 批准的比特币证券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/ex-citi-execs-plan-bitcoin-btc-securities-that-don-t-need-ok-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着对即将批准或拒绝现货比特币 ETF 的猜测达到白热化，一群前花旗集团高管开始提供由最古老的加密货币支持的证券，他们称这种证券不需要美国监管机构的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/ex-citi-execs-plan-bitcoin-btc-securities-that-don-t-need-ok-from-us</guid>
